Package: pgdumper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-client-common, postgresql-common, mailx, libdatetime-timezone-perl, libsysadm-install-perl, libdbd-pg-perl
Description: Dumps all databases for a postgres installation to disk
 Installs a script that can dump all postgres databases to disk in preparation
 for them to be backed up. Also installs a cronjob to run this script nightly.
